overview:
Just My Type Transcription offers Internet-based medical transcription services with EMR integration as a means for physicians to document patient encounters accurately and in a productive manner. Whether your facility is large or small, we can handle all your transcription needs.

Our mission is producing the highest quality patient encounter documentation for all specialties while meeting the special needs of our clients, all while meeting and/or exceeding HIPAA requirements. We deliver our clients the leading technology solution that facilitates the entire dictation & transcription process from start to finish!

What makes us different? Our quality is unsurpassed. Many companies tout 98% accuracy. That’s not good enough for us; we deliver 99.9% accuracy.

We cater to each client and use their current workflow to improve and streamline daily tasks by offering electronic signature, auto-fax and many other features.
